‘Game Of Thrones’ Author Is Taking On TV Werewolves Next 
Published By: MTV - Today 
George R.R. Martin's novella "The Skin Trades" has been optioned by Cinemax, but GRRM won't have as much to do with it as "Game of Thrones."...
